{"text_id":182941,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigated"," entanglement"," increase"," from"," local"," interactions"," with"," not","-","completely","-","positive"," maps","."," Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," lies"," in"," understanding"," how"," local"," interactions"," can"," impact"," the"," entanglement"," properties"," of"," composite"," quantum"," systems",","," with"," the"," aim"," to"," develop"," strategies"," for"," preserving"," and"," enhancing"," entanglement"," under"," highly"," noisy"," and"," imperfect"," conditions","."," Our"," key"," idea"," is"," to"," exploit"," the"," power"," of"," not","-","completely","-","positive"," maps",","," which"," enable"," the"," transformation"," of"," initially"," separable"," states"," into"," entangled"," ones","."," We"," used"," both"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," techniques"," to"," investigate"," this"," phenomenon",".","Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," entanglement"," increase"," through"," local"," interactions"," with"," not","-","completely","-","positive"," maps"," is"," quite"," robust"," against"," several"," noise"," sources",","," such"," as"," deco","herence",","," depolar","izing"," channels",","," and"," amplitude"," damping",","," indicating"," that"," such"," maps"," can"," be"," employed"," for"," entanglement"," generation"," under"," realistic"," experimental"," conditions","."," Moreover",","," we"," found"," that"," the"," entanglement"," increase"," depends"," on"," the"," initial"," state"," of"," the"," system"," and"," the"," specific"," properties"," of"," the"," not","-","completely","-","positive"," maps","."," Our"," methodology"," involved"," the"," use"," of"," tools"," from"," quantum"," information"," theory",","," such"," as"," the"," partial"," transpose"," and"," entanglement"," witnesses",","," to"," quantify"," entanglement","."," Overall",","," our"," findings"," shed"," light"," on"," the"," fundamental"," role"," of"," local"," interactions"," with"," not","-","completely","-","positive"," maps"," in"," generating"," and"," enhancing"," entanglement",","," and"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," for"," the"," design"," of"," quantum"," communication"," and"," computation"," protocols","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}